quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  57,1,"Kala tagoore Allah wonnde ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Mo laЙ“Й“inii Mo. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o Mo fooletaake, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e tagu Mun, e eЙ“Й“oore Mun."
  57,2,"Ko Kanko tun heeranii laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna Mo O muuyani nguurndam, O wara Mo O muuyani maayde. Kanko ko O hattanЙ—o kala huunde. Fii huunde ronkintaa Mo."
  57,3,"Ko Kanko woni Arano Mo goЙ—Й—um aditaaki, SakkitiiЙ—o Mo goЙ—Й—um arataa Й“aawo Mun, FeeГұuЙ—o Mo goЙ—Й—um alaa dow Mun, WirniiЙ—o Mo goЙ—Й—um alaa senngo ley Mun. Kanko ko O annduЙ—o kala huunde. Huunde laawotaako Mo."
  57,4,"Ko Kanko tagiri kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin nder balЙ—e jeegoo, Гұalnde Й—um fuЙ—Й—ornoo e Alet, lanniri e Jumaare, e hoore non Himo waawunoo tagude Й—in ko Й“uri Й—um famЙ—irde yeru hinЖҙaango. Refti O toowi O fotondiri ka dow "Arsi" no O hanndiri. Himo Anndi kala ko naatata e leydi ndin; immorde e ndiyam, e puЙ—i ekw, e kala ko yaltata e mayri; immorde e puЙ—i, e oogirЙ—e ekw, e kala ko jipporta ka kammu; immorde e toЙ“o, e wahayu ekw, e kala ko Жҙawata e maggu; immorde e Malaa'ika, e golle jeyaaЙ“e Й“en e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Himo wonndiri e mon anndal Makko, nokku kala ka wonЙ—on, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e. Huunde e fii mon suuЙ—aaki Mo. Allah no reeni ko golloton ko. Huunde e mun wirnanaaki Mo. O yoЙ“itoyay on Й—um."
  57,5,"Ko Kanko tun heeranii laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko ka Makko tun kadi woni ko fiyakuuji Й—in ruttetee, O Гұaawa tagoore nden Г‘alnde Darngal, O warjooЙ“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  57,6,"Himo naada jemma on e nder Гұalorma on fii no niЙ“Й“itira yimЙ“e Й“en Й—aanoo, O naadira kadi Гұalorma on e nder jemma on fii no ndaygira yimЙ“e Й“en yalta golle. Kanko ko O annduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—um."
  57,7,"GomЙ—inee Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko On, nafqon jawdi ndi Allah waЙ—iri on ndin lomtinaaЙ“e e mun, hiЙ—on yiilira ndi no Allah sar'inirani on. GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Allah e mo'on, Й“e wintii jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e laawol Allah, hino woodani Й“en mbarjaari mawnundi ka Makko, ndin le ko Aljanna."
  57,8,"E ko haЙ—i on gomЙ—ingol Allah? E hino NulaaЙ—o on hino nodda on e Allah, jortagol nde gomЙ—inton Joomi mon seniiЙ—o On. GomЙ—ii le Allah Жҙetti e mon ahadi, nde gomЙ—inton Mo, fewndo O yaltinirnoo on e keeci baabiraaЙ“e mon, si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e."
  57,9,"Ko Kanko woni jippinoowo e jeyaaЙ—o Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e, fii no o yaltinira on e niЙ“e keeferaaku e majjere faade e ndaygu gomЙ—inal e ganndal. Pellet, Allah ko Yurminoowo on, HinnotooЙ—o On. Tawde O nulii Annabaajo Makko on e mon, ko fewna on wewlina."
  57,10,"E ko haЙ—ata on sakkagol fii laawol Allah ngol? E hino le ko Allah heeranii ronugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Fotataa e mon, onon muumini'en, Й“en sakkinooЙ“e jawle mun fii laawol Allah ngol Й—aЙ“Й“irgol welayee Makko ado uddital Makkah ngal Й“e haЙ“idi e heeferЙ“e Й“en fii Й“amtugol Lislaamu, Й“en fotataa e sakkiiЙ“e Й“en Й“aawo uddital ngal Й“e haЙ“idi e heeferЙ“e Й“en. Ko sakkinooЙ“e Й“en ado uddital ngal Й“e haЙ“idaa fii Й“amtugol laawol Allah ngol, Й“uri mawnude maqaama ka Allah, Й“uri kadi darja e dii sakkiiЙ“e jawle mun Й“en Й“aawo mun Й“e haЙ“idaa. ЖҒe fow maЙ“Й“e non, Allah fodii Й“e Aljanna. Allah no humpitii ko golloton kon. Huunde e mun suuЙ—aaki Mo. O yoЙ“itoyay on Й—um."
  57,11,"ko hommbo tottirta jawdi laЙ“undi ndin fii Allah, Allah warjora mo Й—um jawdi sowaandi, hara kadi hino woodani mbarjaari mawndi Г‘alnde Darngal, woni Aljanna?"
  57,12,"Г‘alnde yi'oytaa gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—imЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, hara annoora maЙ“Й“e on no yaara yeeso maЙ“Й“e e Гұaamo maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'anee nden Гұalnde : weltaare mon nden hannde, ko Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley kuЙ“eeje mun e leЙ—Й—e mun, ko on duumotooЙ“e nder ton poomaa. Ko ndin njoЙ“di Й—on woni maloore mawnde nde sugu mun alaa."
  57,13,"Г‘alnde naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en wi'anoyta gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en : habbee men, men ndayginora annoora mon on fii lummbugol siraate. ЖҒe wi'anee jalkiteede : Yiltoree Й“aawo mon, Й—aЙ“Й“iroyon ton ko ndayginoron. Heedo waЙ—ee hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, hara ko jogiingo damal, tawa nder maggal on no fewtiri gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en yurmeende, Й“aawo on fewtiri naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en lepte."
  57,14,"NaafiqiiЙ“e Й“en noddoya muumini en, Й“e wi'a Й“e :E men wondaano e mon ka lislaamu e ka Й—oftaare? JuulЙ“e Й“en jaaboo Й“e : Ko non woniri, hari ko enen. Ko woni tun, on fitinirno ko'e mon naafiqaaku, Й—um bonni fii mon, habbitaniЙ—on gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fooleede fii no feГұГұiniron keefee- ru mon, sikkitiЙ—on si Allah wallay gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, sikkitiЙ—on kadi fii ummital caggal maayde, yelaaji penaale hodi on haa maayde juhi on e mun. Seytaane hodi e moЖҙЖҙere Allah nden."
  57,15,"Hannde on, onon Й“ee naafiqiiЙ“e on jaЙ“antaake soktorЙ—um lepte Allah Й—en, wanaa feГұГұimЙ“e keeferaaku Й“en kadi jaЙ“antee Й—um. Depporde mon nden onon e maЙ“Й“e, ko ka Yiite : ko ngen hanndi e mon. Nge bonii ruttorde."
  57,16,"Hara yontaali gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, nde Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hecciЙ—ira jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippinaa ka Alqur'aanaare immorde e fodooje e kammba? Hara Й“e wa'aali wa Alyahuuda okkanooЙ“e Tawreeta Й“en e Annasaare okkanooЙ“e Linnjiila Й“en e yoorugol Й“erЙ—e. Dumunna juuti hakkunde maЙ“Й“e e nuleede Annabiijo maЙ“Й“e on, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yoori sabu Й—um, ko Й—uuЙ—unoo e maЙ“Й“e kon, hari ko yaltuЙ“e e Й—oftaare Allah, unii e yeddugol Mo."
  57,17,"Anndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay leydi ndin fuЙ—ingol ndi si ndi yoorii. GomЙ—ii Men Й“annginiranii on onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, dalilaaji e hujjaaji fii kattal Allah e gootaagu Makko ngun, fii no haqqiliron, anndon wonnde wuurnituЙ—o ndin leydi On, ko hattanЙ—o wuurnitugol on si on maayii, ko non kadi O waawiri haccinde Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en si Й—e yoorii."
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotooЙ“e yoga e jawle mun Й“en ka worЙ“e e ka rewЙ“e, wintorayЙ“e Й—e Й“ernde laaЙ“unde hara wanaa fii feere alaa, Й“en sowanoyte mbarjaari golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en : sappo kala yeru mun, haa hewtoya teemeЙ—Й—e jeeЙ—iЙ—i cowanЙ—e Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e, hara hino woodani Й“e mbarjaari mawndi ka Allah, woni Aljanna."
  57,19,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko nn Й“e senndaali Й—um, ko Й“en woni siforЙ“e goonguugol. SahimbinaaЙ“e Й“en ka Joomi mun, hino woodani Й“en mbarjaari maЙ“Й“e maranaaЙ“e ndi Й“en e annoora ndaygiroyaЙ—o yeeso e Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal. ЖҒen non yedduЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Й“e woni e fennugol Aayeeje jippinaaЙ—e Й—en e NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Jahiimi ngen. ЖҒe naatoyat e magge Г‘alnde Darngal, ko Й“e luttata poomaa."
  57,20,"Anndee wonnde Й—am nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru Й“alli e welo-welo Й“erЙ—e, e cuЙ—aari mon, e mantagol hakkunde mon fii laamu e dakamme, Й“urodira Й—uuЙ—ugol jawle e Й“iЙ—Й“e. ЖҠum no wa'i wa toЙ“o haawnayngo remooЙ“e Й“en e puЙ—i mun, refti Й—in puЙ—i kecci yoora ko yaawi, yi'aa Й—um an ndaaroowo on, hino wonta ko soyЙ—i, refti Allah muncita fii mun wonta kelon kelon. Hino ka laakara, lette saЙ—tuЙ—e wonannde heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqi'en, e yaafuyee immmorde ka Allah wonannde bakkatuuji jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e welayee Makko. Awa Й—am nguurdam aduna wonaali, si wanaa dakamme lannoowo. Kala suЙ“iiЙ—o on dakamme lannoowo e hoore neema laakara on, haray on Й—on ko sooyuЙ—o koomtaaЙ—o."
  57,21,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, adondiree e golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—e daГұirton yaafaneede junuubi ka Joomi mon: immorde e tuubugol maa kala golle Й“aЙ—torЙ—e Allah ekw, e no heЙ“iron Allah mo yaajeendi mun wa'i wa yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Ngal keЙ“al ko Й“ural Allah ngal O okkata mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Allah ko Jom Й“ural mawnungal e dow jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en."
  57,22,"Bone woo heЙ“ataa yimЙ“e Й“en ka leydi immorde e kokke m. kw. wanaa ko memata Й“e e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й—um tabitananooma ka Alluwal reenaanagl, ado Men tagude ndee tagoore. Pellet, Й—um ko ko newanii Allah."
  57,23,"ЖҠum ko fii wata onon Й“ee yimЙ“e wata on suno e ko laawii on kon, hara kadi on weltoraali neema ko O neemini e mon kon fantinon. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa kala ГұaaЖҙoroowo mantoro ko Allah okki mo kon e hoore yimЙ“e Й“en."
  57,24,"ЖҒen wuddirooЙ“e ko Й“e haani okkude kon, Й“e yamira kadi yimЙ“e Й“en nguddam, ko hayruЙ“e. Kala Й—uurniiЙ—o e Й—oftagol Allah, Й—um ko kanko lorrata, wanaa doo Allah. Pellet, Allah kan ko Galo Mo hatonjinaa e Й—oftaare jeyaaЙ“e Makko, YettiniiЙ—o e kala fiyaaku."
  57,25,"Sellii Men nulirii NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en hujjaaji Й“annguЙ—i, Men jippindinani Й“e Defte e sariyaare, fii no yimЙ“e Й“en ГұiiЙ“ira e nunЙ—al. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tiiЙ—uЙ—e woni e mun; ko kayri tafirЙ—e jogaaji, ko non kadi nafooje wonirani yimЙ“e Й“en e majje ka mecce maЙ“Й“e, e fii kadi no Allah anndira anndal feГұГұinirangol jeyaaЙ“e Й“en, Й“en wallooЙ“e Mo e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en ka wirnii. Pelelt, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, FooluЙ—o Mo fooletaake. Fii huunde ronkinЕӢtaa Mo."
  57,26,"GomЙ—ii Men nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima (yo Й“e his), Men waЙ—i e geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol Annabaaku e Defte tellinaaЙ—e. Hino jeyanoo e geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol feewuЙ“e e laawol foccingol ngol, hawri e peewal, ko Й—uuЙ—unoo kon e maЙ“Й“e ko yaltunooЙ“e e Й—fotaare Allah."
  57,27,"Refti Men jokkintini Й“e NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, Men nuliri Й“e kala e mofte mun. Men jokkintiniri Й“e Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama on, Men okki mo Linjiila, Men waЙ—i e Й“erЙ—e gomЙ—imЙ“e mo Й“en jokki mo : yurmeende e giggol, Й“e yiЙ—indiri Й“e yurmondiri. ЖҒe sincoyi fantingol ka diina maЙ“Й“e, Й“e acci yoga e ko Allah daginannoo Й“e immorde e desal e dakamme, e hoore Men Й—aЙ“Й“iraa Й“e Й—um, ko kamЙ“e fawitii Й—um sincugol ka diina. Ko Men Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo Й“e Menen, ko jokkugol welayee Allah on, kono Й“e waЙ—aali Й—um. Men okki mbarjaari gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й—uuЙ—unoo kon e maЙ“Й“e, ko yaltirnooЙ“e e Й—oftaare Allah fennugol ko NulaaЙ—o Muhammadu addunoo kon."
  57,28,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah gollitiri sari'a Makko on ! Huliree Allah Й—oftagol yamaruyeeji Makko Й—in, woЙ—Й—itoo e haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in, gomЙ—inon NulaaЙ—o Makko on; O okkay on geЙ“e Й—iЙ—i e mbarjaari gomЙ—ingol mon ngol Muhammadu e NulaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e Й“en, O waЙ—ana on kadi annoora Й“e ndayginorton ka aduna mon e ka lummboygol Siraate Г‘alnde Darngal, O haforana on kadi bakkatuuji mon Й—in hara O nanngitirtaa on Й—i. Pellet, Allah seniiЙ—o On, ko Haforanoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  57,29,"Ko Men Й“annginirani on Й“ural Amen mawngal ngal e kon ko Men marani on onon muumuni'en, immorde e mbrajaari sowaandi, ko fii no Alyahhuda e Annasaara ka yimЙ“e Defte anndira wonnde Й“e hattanaa hay huunde e Й“ural Allah ngal, sakko Й“e yeЙ—a mo Й“e yiЙ—ani, Й“e Й—awa ngal mo Й“e yiЙ—i Й—awude, Й“e annda kadi pellet, Й“ural ngal ko e juuЙ—e Allah woni, Himo yeЙ—a ngal mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Pellet, Allah ko Jom Й“ural mawngal ngal O heertinanta mo O muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
